{"tid":230743,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日我被困於巴士內","createTime":"2017-05-05T14:41:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-08T04:26:15.000Z","uid":114590,"like":3,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"16072a585bcc4d58a6d4fb4aa2ac7f96176be7d2","tid":230743,"uid":114590,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:41:29.000Z","msg":"今日因為太好訓，到總站都唔識落車。因為坐上層後面嘅關係，司機發現唔到我就落咗車。其實我之前都試過訓到唔知醒，但每次都有司機叫我落車，但今日我第一次訓到自然醒。咁我醒咗之後，就落下層啦，發現巴士閂埋太平門，我諗咗兩個解決方案:<br />\n一、拍門。但因為旺角東太多人，我怕太樣衰，我放棄咗。<br />\n二、禁緊急掣開太平門。但我發現我唔太緊張，咁我就决定坐低等。<br />\n<br />\n最後我google 咗「點打開巴士門」，但我發現嘜都揾唔到！當我崩潰到係巴士唱彌敦道同狗叫嘅時候，有個車長嚟開車，拯救咗我。係啲個時候，我衝咗岀車。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a551ede934b701bd6c16ec60afb4f64d6100f976","tid":230743,"uid":114590,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:43:16.000Z","msg":"樓主自推"},{"pid":"fa87a248baf67ba661cf272ca445f137e0eadac2","tid":230743,"uid":114590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:43:48.000Z","msg":"推呀推，弗弗西斯推石咁推"},{"pid":"7305462fc7ff49736eb14d7d2311943141fc7e08","tid":230743,"uid":98645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:53:32.000Z","msg":"尾班咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 下班車開佢一定會開番門"},{"pid":"44ea076db15c080dc61145411b39f173f66e7e4e","tid":230743,"uid":32925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T15:02:40.000Z","msg":"我都試過<br />\n不過好彩識去司機位搵到開太平門個制自己開門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e8ccd3790ce7a3caaa6af1bd7ed628f1944316c","tid":230743,"uid":97482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T15:07:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都試過<br />\n不過好彩識去司機位搵到開太平門個制自己開門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br 