if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家99%專利巴士都係禁紅綠掣嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁佢點上車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗佢個意思個新式車外面果度一樣都開到，不過係紅綠制唔係扭制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09d64c7059d08de3b88f3c3919ec2159528638ec","tid":230743,"uid":45872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T17:27:39.000Z","msg":"我都試過 個陣初中唔識開門係車入面鳩試 咁啱門外有個𡃁仔見到我 好熟手咁係出面幫我開門 個刻真係柒到仆街 講聲唔該就急急腳走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c10585a1f716e866342d4a2b5ab19d8dc3b6e931","tid":230743,"uid":43213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T17:34:59.000Z","msg":"以前細個 巴士仲係熱狗嗰陣 <br />\n試過好似你咁訓著左 最後係樓下開窗想爬出去<br />\n結果卡撚住左 等啲清潔姐姐發現我抆番我出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07e7b7ee712d742edfa2b744fefda1f8b1e71fbd","tid":230743,"uid":114590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T17:41:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前細個 巴士仲係熱狗嗰陣 <br />\n試過好似你咁訓著左 最後係樓下開窗想爬出去<br />\n結果卡撚住左 等啲清潔姐姐發現我抆番我出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁咪柒到世界盡頭，有無上報紙。"},{"pid":"6d3da73467dc193b0da9bb18a0e4105a922992da","tid":230743,"uid":114590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T17:42:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過同樓主一樣唔知醒冇人嗌<br />\n企係門邊等左陣有司機見到開門救我<br />\n一打開門個司機就問我 咩事呀先生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我屌 你想我點答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不要問我從哪裡來......"},{"pid":"d64a249209e7cb1a457a57771ae1556d2d677869","tid":230743,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim