sire</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/WYcIyFF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FWYcIyFF.png&h=988f92d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/UDQxEJg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FUDQxEJg.png&h=3a1b5ff3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n熄左大掣好似真係開唔到門<br />\n不過熄得大掣多數番左廠, 到時開電筒慢慢搵大掣, 直到有工程部問你喺巴士做乜 你咪照講你訓過龍</blockquote><br />\n緊急掣，熄左大掣都開到。<br />\n唔係司機點走，第2日司機點上車呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係巴士總站見過司機出左黎 係巴士門隔離有個制係扭<br />\n佢扭一下道門就關左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好懶醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個制係巴士出面架<br />\n係巴士入邊點樣出去開門呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae9aacfff4792e028dad03a2f0f93aa9e987feb6","tid":230743,"uid":80763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T01:45:05.000Z","msg":"出口門頂會有個手制開門<br />\n出左去之後記得係出面<br />\n銀色半圓度拉番個制關門<br />\n<br />\n利申 老豆巴士佬"},{"pid":"141745da7765f9e5eabc58a5e14482fd67539ec6","tid":230743,"uid":60850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T03:34:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解樓豬唔打爆玻璃逃生?</blockquote><br />\n話曬都係個文人，無豬肉兄咁粗暴。</blockquote><br />\n其實可以直接揸走架車</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20130624/18310005\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20130624%2F18310005&d=3wrM%2FJom4zLweqSprMIx0pWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=542ef709\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20130624%2F18310005&h=c7ed8b93\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20130624/18310005</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></b